                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Even boḥan</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אבן בוחן</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>An anti-Christian polemical treatise, based on Sefer milḥamot ha-Shem of Jacob ben Reuben. Incomplete by the scribe. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
